<doc f='llvm/llvm/lib/Target/PowerPC/PPCISelLowering.cpp' l='9212'>/// LowerROTL - Custom lowering for ROTL(v1i128) to vector_shuffle(v16i8).
/// We lower ROTL(v1i128) to vector_shuffle(v16i8) only if shift amount is
/// a multiple of 8. Otherwise convert it to a scalar rotation(i128)
/// i.e (or (shl x, C1), (srl x, 128-C1)).</doc>
